        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、需要安装requests<br>
1、Windows键+R，回车。输入cmd<br>
<img src="https://xicheng100.github.io/post-images/1585312102617.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
2、输入pip install requests<br>
<img src="https://xicheng100.github.io/post-images/1585312109853.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
二、程序<br>
import requests<br>
pic = requests.get('https://p.ssl.qhimg.com/dmsmty/74_74_100/t0117cd78b141e0bfa2.png')#在你需要的爬取的网页F12、ctrl+shift+c、点击你需要的图片找到src=“”里面的<br>
with open('python.png','wb') as f:#保存的文件名<br>
f.write(pic.content)<br>
<img src="https://xicheng100.github.io/post-images/1585312686306.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
三、就会生成一个.png的文件</p>
